HANEY V. THE STATE. Abusive and Insulting Language. 42 South. 683.) Appeal from Cleburne County Court. *676Burton & McMahan, for appellant. Massey Wilson, Attorney General, for appellee. Weakley, C. J., Haralson and Denson, JJ., concur.

(Decided Dec. 5th, 1906.

Heard before Hon. T. A. Johnson.

Affirmed.
